These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
City: san-francisco, liverpool
2 different pets are kept: snake, ferret
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, pear
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, techno
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| City       | liverpool       | san-francisco |
| Pet         | ferret | snake  |
| Food       | pear    | cabbage    |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | dubstep      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
House: cape-cod, farmhouse
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rat
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, punk
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| House      | farmhouse     | cape-cod |
| Pet           | lizard | rat      |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | electronic      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | reading     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, november
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, cricket
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the teacher##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby      | board-games | magic-tricks  |
| Birthday          | december    | november   |
| Sport   | cricket  | baseball   |
| Job     | teacher     | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
City: colone, paris
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, scooter
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, green
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani
1. the chinese is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to paris is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| City      | colone       | paris |
| Transport          | scooter         | car    |
| Color           | green | black    |
| Nationality   | chinese           | pakistani   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bluemaster
There 2 different types of food: pear, lemon
City: liverpool, boston
There are 2 different nationalities: german, chinese
1. the person eating pear is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the chinese##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Cigar         | havana | bluemaster   |
| Food   | pear | lemon       |
| City         | liverpool   | boston |
| Nationality     | chinese    | german     |

