2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat
2 different games are played: scrabble, whist
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, brazilian
1. the brazilian is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| House   | futuristic         | farmhouse    |
| Cigar       | baccarat     | vegafina  |
| Game      | scrabble | whist     |
| Nationality        | brazilian     | australian |

