.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, spanish
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, metal
2 different games are played: billiard, chess
House: cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the chinese is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the chinese is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the person playing billiard is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | spanish | chinese     |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | metal |
| Game           | billiard          | chess    |
| House     | ranch-style            | cape-cod       |

 